    <ul style="list-style-type:disc">

            <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span

                style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">div</span></span><span
                style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">来表示页面章节，但是这些</span></span><span

        </li>
    </ul>
    <p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>

    <p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">使用语义化标签有以下优点：</span></span></p>
    <ol style="list-style-type: decimal; margin-left: 40px;">
        <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">更好的呈现出内容结构</span></span></li>
        <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">有利于</span></span>
            <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SEO</span></span> <span
                style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">优化</span></span>
        </li>
        <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">语义化使得代码更具有可读性，让其他开发人员更加理解你的</span></span><span
                style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">html</span></span><span
                style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">结构，减少差异化。</span></span></li>
    </ol>
    <p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
    <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
        <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">尽管音视频时代大部分标签已经有更好的优化方案，但是部分标签仍然有一定的参考价值，例如</span></span><span
                style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> &lt;header&gt;
